item.title: CVE-2017-3215|2024-08-05T14:16:28.255Z -- milwaukee%20tool -- one-key
item.description: The Milwaukee ONE-KEY Android mobile application uses bearer tokens with an expiration of one year. This bearer token, in combination with a user_id can be used to perform user actions.
